      "description": "### Changelog v3.0.0\r\n\r\n#### Features\r\n* **i18n**: Add support for internationalization. (`aece666`)\r\n* **Editor**: Allow editing the mind map directly when using Mind-Elixir plaintext format. (`e674084`)\r\n\r\n#### Bug Fixes\r\n* **Parser**: Improve Mind-Elixir plaintext recognition. (`db0c344`)\r\n* **Parser**: Skip `thematicBreak` (horizontal rules) during markdown parsing to prevent unexpected behavior. (`de575bd`)\r\n\r\n#### Refactoring\r\n* **Parser**: Simplify `processList` logic in the markdown parser. (`451139a`)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SSShooter/obsidian-mindmap/compare/2.0.0...3.0.0",
